{"tid":2150922,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企人戶口比人利用","createTime":"2020-08-11T06:47:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T07:47:55.000Z","uid":252320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6686aaba1e1295ad61ab6c3740904e948e5ff523","tid":2150922,"uid":252320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:47:29.000Z","msg":"話說我家姐痕身戶口忽然比人凍結左<br />\n之後差佬打黎話我家姐戶口係一個網上訂購口罩嘅帳戶<br />\n有人過完數收唔到口罩報警，但佢無做過呢啲野<br />\n差佬話要上屋企搜證，我家姐屋企有大有細好多人再加上疫情關係唔方便<br />\n依家應該點樣證明佢清白<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n暫時約左上警署落口供"},{"pid":"07d88daadf967e3a4bdd0aee0ca9830f798e6bf7","tid":2150922,"uid":128522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:49:06.000Z","msg":"銀行RECORD<br />\n對返出入帳"},{"pid":"264c490b4c4a41253d3eff72d6ab9f50e4e077b4","tid":2150922,"uid":43530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:49:33.000Z","msg":"叫銀行出返張月結單？"},{"pid":"3ea7ae4d5f8eb512985584f33035207926cb98b7","tid":2150922,"uid":252320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:51:01.000Z","msg":"依家佢戶口凍結左網上睇唔到，落分行佢地會唔會都係話凍結左唔比睇？"},{"pid":"a854a47ab2102bcf919a36654f169074234c36b4","tid":2150922,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:53:26.000Z","msg":"問下你家姐有無借過戶口俾人啦<br />\n有心呃錢嘅點會叫人入落一個自己拎唔到錢嘅戶口<br />\n除非你家姐係俾人玩"},{"pid":"2ee7aba7948b1cf9fa18af9c937c9bd12366223f","tid":2150922,"uid":174013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:53:43.000Z","msg":"無啦啦會有人扮賣口罩,然後叫人入錢落你家姐ACC送錢比你家姐洗?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就唔撚信呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a92bf41bcb79950df7a3adbac51962e0f31ea8e","tid":2150922,"uid":78374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T07:20:14.000Z","msg":"樓主不如講真話啦<br />\n好嗎?"},{"pid":"de3909d0fd332b7b01f273aa3742e0c9265eb8c5","tid":2150922,"uid":263485,"like":0,"dislike":3,"sc